headline: How Dossier’s Exclusive Fragrance Launch at Target (TGT) Has Changed Its Investment Story
summary: Dossier announced its entry into Target’s nationwide stores and online platform, making select bestsellers and exclusive new launches available, highlighted by a two-month exclusive on the “It Factor” perfume and prominent in-store displays through February 2026. This partnership brings a high-profile, influencer-led fragrance campaign into Target’s beauty aisles, expanding the retailer’s portfolio of exclusive and differentiated offerings during the key holiday shopping season.
